                <h1>Lt. Gov. Justin Fairfax, a Duke alum, faces sexual assault allegation as Virginia politics scramble</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/c125f06c-e666-474e-bb18-04f1836c0bbb.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Courtesy&#x20;of&#x20;Wikimedia&#x20;Commons" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
